    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      235.72,
      523.37,
      276.6
    ],
    "text": "On the evening of 10 May 2026, the Wellawaya Police Station initiated investigations following a report of a suspicious death in a paddy field in the Sinnawatte area of the Wellawaya Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      291.16,
      407.71,
      304.44
    ],
    "text": "The deceased is a 53-year-old resident of the Sinnawatte area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      318.88,
      505.62,
      345.96
    ],
    "text": "Ongoing investigations have revealed that the deceased had been reported missing since 8 May 2026 prior to the discovery of the body.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
