    "text": "On the evening of 10 May 2026, officers from the Police Special Task Force Jayawardenapura Camp conducted a raid in the Kahawita area of the Attidiya Police Division under Mount Lavinia jurisdiction and arrested a suspect in possession of 76 grams and 100 milligrams of crystal methamphetamine (\u201cIce\u201d).",
